column5: Anyone know if the boat ramp is accessible in Dalhousie yet, or is the Niagara the only option for now?  Time to clear the cob webs from the outboard!
Thanks! Hopefully the weather cooperates for Wednesday.
The docks might not be there...Makes it tough to launch alone.
There's one dock in the water, you'll be good to go.
The G&F always leave in one dock for emergency services. Ramp was in use over the weekend.
